articles.title: Fortnite's new Jujutsu Kaisen anime collab adds themed outfits and quests - The Verge
articles.description: Fortnite’s new v25.30 update released Tuesday adds a new anime crossover with Jujutsu Kaisen. It’s just the latest anime-themed event to take place in Epic Games’ battle royale hit.
